817
00:59:22,170 --> 00:59:26,260
Let us-a not waste-a
time standing here
talking about it, Captain.

818
00:59:35,100 --> 00:59:38,010
I can't believe
we're stealing a jet.

819
00:59:38,060 --> 00:59:39,270
