we will be far away.

829
01:00:16,920 --> 01:00:18,920
The fate of the world
hangs in the balance.

830
01:00:18,970 --> 01:00:22,060
I have finally pieced
together his master plan.

831
01:00:22,100 --> 01:00:24,060
Master plan?

832
01:00:24,100 --> 01:00:27,280
