of a script doctor, Mo.

833
01:00:27,320 --> 01:00:28,930
Script doctor?

834
01:00:28,980 --> 01:00:31,020
Go on.

835
01:00:31,070 --> 01:00:33,370
Why is he trying
to resurrect his wife?

836
01:00:33,420 --> 01:00:35,980
That is not an option.

837
