I'm so dead.

870
01:02:16,690 --> 01:02:20,260
Oh, the Borealis Stone.

871
01:02:20,310 --> 01:02:22,390
The lay lines
on the ancient map

872
01:02:22,440 --> 01:02:23,870
all led here.

873
01:02:23,920 --> 01:02:26,880
The hardest totemic
icon to find

