plant the explosives.

918
01:05:16,090 --> 01:05:18,830
Cut and print.

919
01:05:18,870 --> 01:05:21,180
That's a wrap.

920
01:05:21,220 --> 01:05:23,660
Now it's up
to you, Mosaic,

921
01:05:23,710 --> 01:05:25,930
