out of here alive.

922
01:05:25,970 --> 01:05:27,100
Aah!

923
01:05:55,520 --> 01:05:58,650
Thank you, son.
I couldn't have... Huh?

924
01:06:00,260 --> 01:06:03,090
Oh, my sweet Lord.

925
01:06:16,540 --> 01:06:18,850
Next!

926
01:06:33,730 --> 01:06:37,170
