to be different.

963
01:08:53,790 --> 01:08:55,920
To make a difference.

964
01:08:55,960 --> 01:08:58,310
Come in!

965
01:08:58,350 --> 01:09:01,270
I brought you a double
caramel mocha frap.

966
01:09:01,310 --> 01:09:03,400
