knew how you felt.

974
01:09:19,290 --> 01:09:22,160
Oh, I think
I can imagine.

975
01:09:22,200 --> 01:09:23,160
Mags.

976
01:09:23,210 --> 01:09:25,510
Why didn't you tell me?

977
01:09:25,560 --> 01:09:26,860
Tell you what?

978
01:09:30,470 --> 01:09:34,570
Oh, that. Did you
expect anything less?

979
01:09:34,610 --> 01:09:38,350
